algorithm

类 ActiveLearning

  • java.lang.Object
    • algorithm.ActiveLearning
  • 直接已知子类:
    ClusteringBasedActiveLearning

    public class ActiveLearning
extends java.lang.Object
    The superclass of any active learning algorithm. Read the data, compute the accuracy, get misclassified ones.

    Author: Fan Min minfanphd@163.com, minfan@swpu.edu.cn
    Copyright: The source code and all documents are open and free. PLEASE keep this header while revising the program.
    Organization: Lab of Machine Learning, Southwest Petroleum University, Chengdu 610500, China.
    Project: The cost-sensitive active learning project.

    Progress: Almost finished, further revision is possible.
    Written time: July 20, 2019.
    Last modify time: July 21, 2019.

      • getMisclassified

        public int[] getMisclassified(int paraStatus)
        Get misclassified instances in "pure" blocks. That is because some blocks are not really pure.
        参数:
        paraStatus - The status for checking. It can be PURE_BLOCK_PREDICTED, ONE_NN_PREDICTED, etc.
        返回:
        The indices of instances, such as [5, 16], or empty array [].

      • knnUnhandled

        public void knnUnhandled()
        Classify unhandled instances using kNN.

      • knnUnhandled

        public void knnUnhandled(int paraK)
        Classify unhandled instances using 1NN. The neighbor should be in the same block. In case no label has been queried, the default label will be 0.
        参数:
        paraK - The k value.
